Official Rule Book for the Alphabetical Challenge
-------------------------------------------------

1 - Both Users need to be online at the same time or else it will not count. (Counts for every Chat)
	1.1 - If the User has the 'online' and 'dnd' symbole, its allowed to strike. If they are offline or afk no.
	      Striking while the User is on 'offline' is only allowed if they are writing.
2 - The letters can't be in a single message
3 - Lower case only
4 - No Autohotkeys

